name: "holding the line over hours can be joyful" dedicated to Komachi & Lily
description:
"holding the line over hours can be joyful" 

This 3/3 Items out of the "holding the line over hours can be joyful" Collection called:

Just feel like releasing & dedicate this piece as an Anthem to this great space we host today with @lilynicoleart and @komachidama!
We had a great time with great peoples ...hearing soo deep stories from souls all over the world. It was an honor for me to share such an intensive time together. 
I mint this piece right now after we still holding together the space over 8 hours already...great marathon my ladies. Enjoy it soo much. Hope this piece will reminds you always on this great energy exchange time we share today to each others and to the world. 


"holding the line over hours can be joyful" 

3/3

5762 × 3241

During my time exchanges with the actors i love to capture details and spots on my path. Unforgetable places and epic moments. Sometimes in the simple things we will find the beauty. And as well in moments where you just be on the right second there to catch unique moments is a great feeling too.
